  },
  "dialogue": [
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Damn it.",
      "zh": "該死。",
      "ja": "くそっ。",
      "time": "00:00:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'm lost!",
      "zh": "我迷路了！",
      "ja": "迷子になった！",
      "time": "00:00:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Where's the one?",
      "zh": "那個在哪裡？",
      "ja": "あれはどこ？",
      "time": "00:00:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It's just really...",
      "zh": "真的只是...",
      "ja": "本当にただ...",
      "time": "00:00:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "The one we talk!",
      "zh": "我們說的那個！",
      "ja": "私たちが話しているあれ！",
      "time": "00:00:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hell will be stuck here forever!",
      "zh": "我們會永遠被困在這裡！",
      "ja": "ここに永遠に閉じ込められる！",
      "time": "00:00:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Do not panic!",
      "zh": "不要慌張！",
      "ja": "慌てるな！",
      "time": "00:00:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Do not panic!",
      "zh": "不要慌張！",
      "ja": "慌てるな！",
      "time": "00:00:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "We are trained for professionals!",
      "zh": "我們是受過專業訓練的！",
      "ja": "私たちはプロの訓練を受けている！",
      "time": "00:00:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Now stay calm!",
      "zh": "現在保持冷靜！",
      "ja": "さあ、落ち着け！",
      "time": "00:00:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "We are going around the leaf!",
      "zh": "我們要繞過這片葉子！",
      "ja": "葉っぱの周りを回る！",
      "time": "00:00:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Around the leaf?",
      "zh": "繞過葉子？",
      "ja": "葉っぱの周り？",
      "time": "00:00:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I don't think we can do that.",
      "zh": "我覺得我們做不到。",
      "ja": "それは無理だと思う。",
      "time": "00:00:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh, nonsense!",
      "zh": "哦，胡說！",
      "ja": "おいおい、そんなことない！",
      "time": "00:00:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "This is nothing compared to the twig of 93.",
      "zh": "這跟93年的小枝比起來算不了什麼。",
      "ja": "これは93年の小枝に比べたら何でもない。",
      "time": "00:00:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "That's it!",
      "zh": "就是這樣！",
      "ja": "それだ！",
      "time": "00:00:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "That's it!",
      "zh": "就是這樣！",
      "ja": "それだ！",
      "time": "00:00:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Good!",
      "zh": "好！",
      "ja": "いいぞ！",
      "time": "00:00:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You're doing great!",
      "zh": "你做得很好！",
      "ja": "うまくやってる！",
      "time": "00:00:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "There you go!",
      "zh": "就這樣！",
      "ja": "その調子！",
      "time": "00:00:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Hell you go!",
      "zh": "去吧！",
      "ja": "行け！",
      "time": "00:00:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Watch my eyes!",
      "zh": "看著我的眼睛！",
      "ja": "私の目を見て！",
      "time": "00:00:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Don't look away!",
      "zh": "不要移開視線！",
      "ja": "目をそらすな！",
      "time": "00:00:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And here's the line again!",
      "zh": "線又來了！",
      "ja": "そしてまた線が来た！",
      "time": "00:01:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thank you!",
      "zh": "謝謝！",
      "ja": "ありがとう！",
      "time": "00:01:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thank you, Mr. Soil!",
      "zh": "謝謝你，土先生！",
      "ja": "ありがとう、土さん！",
      "time": "00:01:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Good job, everybody!",
      "zh": "大家做得好！",
      "ja": "みんな、よくやった！",
      "time": "00:01:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh, my, there's quite a gap, Mr. Soil!",
      "zh": "喔，土先生，這裡有很大的空隙！",
      "ja": "おや、土さん、かなり隙間がある！",
      "time": "00:01:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Shouldn't we tell the queen?",
      "zh": "我們不該告訴女王嗎？",
      "ja": "女王に知らせるべきじゃない？",
      "time": "00:01:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I don't think we need to involve the queen in this.",
      "zh": "我覺得不需要讓女王參與這件事。",
      "ja": "これに女王を巻き込む必要はないと思う。",
      "time": "00:01:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "She's got enough on her plate already.",
      "zh": "她已經有很多事情要處理了。",
      "ja": "彼女はもう十分忙しい。",
      "time": "00:01:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Trading her daughter.",
      "zh": "還要把女兒嫁出去。",
      "ja": "娘を嫁がせることもあるし。",
      "time": "00:01:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, yes!",
      "zh": "喔，是啊！",
      "ja": "ああ、そうだね！",
      "time": "00:01:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Princess Adam!",
      "zh": "亞當公主！",
      "ja": "アダム姫！",
      "time": "00:01:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "The poor dear!",
      "zh": "可憐的孩子！",
      "ja": "かわいそうな子！",
      "time": "00:01:19"
    }
  ]
}